### Sağlık Kontrolü
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### ======== ARAÇ ========

### Araç girişi başlat (driverId seed'den gelir, 1-5 arası)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/vehicle/start
Content-Type: application/json

{ "driverId": 1 }

### Araç tamamlandı
POST http://localhost:3001/api/vehicle/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{ "vehicleSessionId": 1 }

### ======== GİRİŞ ========

### Ürün girişi kaydet
POST http://localhost:3001/api/entry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleSessionId": 1,
  "productId": 1,
  "qualityId": 1,
  "caseCount": 10,
  "weight": 125.5,
  "marketId": 3
}

### ======== PAZARLAR ========

### Tüm pazarları listele (pendingCount dahil)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/markets

### Pazar'ın bekleyen girişlerini getir
GET http://localhost:3001/api/markets/3/entries

### ======== ÇIKIŞ ========

### İrsaliye oluştur
POST http://localhost:3001/api/exit
Content-Type: application/json

{ "marketId": 3, "entryIds": [1, 2] }

### ======== ADMIN AUTH ========

### Giriş yap — token'ı kopyala
POST http://localhost:3001/api/admin/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "password": "admin123" }

### ======== ADMIN CRUD (token gerekli) ========

### Şoförleri listele
GET http://localhost:3001/api/admin/drivers
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Şoför ekle
POST http://localhost:3001/api/admin/drivers
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Yeni Şoför" }

### Şoför güncelle
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/admin/drivers/1
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Ahmet Yılmaz (Güncellendi)" }

### Şoför sil
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/admin/drivers/6
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Ürünleri listele
GET http://localhost:3001/api/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Pazarları listele (admin)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/admin/markets
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Pazar ekle
POST http://localhost:3001/api/admin/markets
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{ "no": 21, "name": "Pazar 21" }

### ======== RAPORLAR ========

### Günlük özet
GET http://localhost:3001/api/admin/reports/daily?date=2026-05-02
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Pazar bazlı rapor
GET http://localhost:3001/api/admin/reports/by-market?date=2026-05-02
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Ürün bazlı rapor
GET http://localhost:3001/api/admin/reports/by-product?date=2026-05-02
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Son 7 günün en çok gelenleri
GET http://localhost:3001/api/admin/reports/top-products?days=7&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
